blog.description: Kristen, 20 // i promise that you’ll never find another like ME!

summary: @taylorswift things in my life are starting to get quite hectic again as I get back from my two week long vacation in Australia....
body: @taylorswift things in my life are starting to get quite hectic again as I get back from my two week long vacation in Australia. Things with my jobs are getting difficult as they keep increasing my hours and I’m exhausted from the constant working and lack of free time and I’m trying to plan out how I’m supposed to live in Dublin for three and a half months for the fall school semester and then I need all this stuff for school and nursing and things with my boyfriend are real tough atm….. on the brightside I’ll see you on July 27th at Gillette stadium! Not sure if I’m going with my boyfriend or if I might end up going alone yet …. but I’ll be there! Love you 😘
